snippet.title: Superfighters Deluxe Trailer
snippet.description:
Superfighters Deluxe is a unique action game that combines brawling, shooting and platforming in dynamic sandboxy 2D levels. Lots of weapons and fun gameplay systems interlock to create absurd action-movie chaos.
More at https://SuperfightersDeluxe.com
or https://store.steampowered.com/app/855860/Superfighters_Deluxe/

Design by Johan Hjärpe
Programming by Alexander "Gurt" Siigur
Music by Lucas "Splinter" Casas
Additional music by Han "hzlancer" Zhu

Trailer by Lucas "Splinter" Casas
